ors the hypothesis that this source is a black hole LMXB,\nrather than a neutron star LMXB with significant geometric beaming of its X-ray\nemission.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 26 Apr 2012 00:43:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-04"}
