ll to sustain its protein\nsynthesis machinery, even in the absence of proliferation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 26 Apr 2012 14:31:41 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 9 Jan 2013 23:20:27 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 29 Apr 2019 15:49:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-01-06"}
